{
  "stem": "4686.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or is it a big room?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we can put a bigger family in it, what is two adults and two children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's what you were doing?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were giving them the information about the different houses?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the-- the eyes of the-- of the council, because I had a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was able to run around easy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, by that time, youngster-- young-- the young people were in-- in work battalions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so there were only a few elderly people who were running the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Most-- most probably.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rules are rules.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father always told me that the straight and narrow, that's the way to do it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also, I-- I find myself very important, and I wouldn't-- I wouldn't let people tell me what to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- you know, at 12 years old, it's quite a heavy, heavy thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't any particular problems.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew that, if the siren goes, then you go to the nearest bunker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was summertime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was sunshine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Grandma moves in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't a catastrophic for us kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six, eight weeks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's sister and husband, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Berti, ?] they lived next door to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of their son was in labor camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other one went underground and was a member of the resistance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were trying to catch him, and they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So at the end, one night, they came with two guys and took my auntie and uncle away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then after weeks and weeks, we find out that they are in an inter-- internation--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Inter-- internation-- in--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After interrogation, in a-- in a special camp near Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
